Jim,
Maybe I should open a separate ticket.. but I&#39;ve notice that /getusercert API is truncating string passed in &#34;username&#34; field. For example, I&#39;ve passed a string &#34;Soichi2 Hayashi 238&#34; and it has issued certificate with following subject.

CN = Soichi2
OU = People
O = Open Science Grid
DC = opensciencegrid
DC = org

