Soichi</pre></div><div class='update_description'><i onclick="document.location='27445#1448044353'; reset_anchor();" class="pull-right icon icon-share"></i><div class="header"><time datetime="2015-11-20T18:32:33+00:00">Nov 20, 2015 06:32 PM UTC</time> by <b>Mine Altunay</b><a class="anchor" name="1448044353">&nbsp;</a></div><pre>Soichi,
